graphify-out/

# --- Sassy Butler TTS models (~120 MB, re-downloadable) ---
# Mirrors the standalone Sassy Butler repo, which also keeps these untracked.
# The build REQUIRES them at feature/butler/src/main/assets/tts/. Restore with:
#   cp "<Butler Alarm>/app/src/main/assets/tts/"*.{onnx,bin} feature/butler/src/main/assets/tts/
feature/butler/src/main/assets/tts/*.onnx
feature/butler/src/main/assets/tts/*.bin
